{"tid":2070661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛黨愛國NGO 東華三院籲市民收到1萬元後捐出","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T13:42:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"95fe40493d6cce29961a755d1c721ed4d506acf2","tid":2070661,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"東華三院宣布推出「東華三院‧分享愛‧疫境同行」失業及短期經濟援助籌募計劃，呼籲市民彰顯愛心，支援社會上的貧苦大眾，率先捐出特區政府即將發放的1萬元全數或部分金額，幫助因新型冠狀病毒疫情而失業或收入大受影響者，以及未符合資格領取綜援的低收入家庭。<br />\n<br />\n東華三院表示，目標籌款金額為300萬元，預期協助不少於300個家庭。計劃會收集公眾捐款至8月初，並將於7月起供有需要者申請，每個獲批的家庭可獲最多1萬元資助金額。<br />\n<br />\n東華三院呼籲各界企業支持此項計劃，除以公司名義捐款外，亦可鼓勵員工及其家屬一同響應，為有需要的人伸出援手，同心協力跨過逆境。市民如欲支持是次計劃，可登入東華三院網站按指示捐款。"},{"pid":"5e475a04d0495120d06925d527089dea0edd4210","tid":2070661,"uid":108201,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"NGO快d收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYVBzhW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYVBzhW.gif&h=75c72f3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e051850e3d0fcf6bb5f3addff1b4060e0995e20d","tid":2070661,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"哦！得啦！等下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2706a08eaea1a12bd9f4d426f456db9c36433f","tid":2070661,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"下世啦"},{"pid":"f996c9b86955b689b203a8ec5c39be61e90e33f2","tid":2070661,"uid":76680,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"就派錢間間NGO都出黎搶錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c339d6d8b40a665936e3b0d93e53fe31b3bd1b1","tid":2070661,"uid":8880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cit